Date: 1997-02-16

Title: Vortex solutions of parity and time reversal invariant

Maxwell-Dirac-Chern-Simons gauge theoryAuthors: Junsoo Shin

Comments: 10pages, revtex

We construct parity and time reversal invariant Maxwell-Chern-Simons gaugetheory coupled to fermions with adding the parity partner to the matter and thegauge fields, which can give nontopological vortex solutions depending on thesign of the Chern-Simons coupling constant.